OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAfter a
OL,6,Fmostly clear start, patchy low cloud
OL,7,Fwill develop later in the night, along
OL,8,Fwith areas of mist and fog. Chilly,
OL,9,Fwith an isolated frost possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FPatchy early low cloud, mist
OL,12,Fand fog will soon clear to give
OL,13,Fanother fine and dry day with long
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Mild inland, but cooler
OL,15,Ftowards the east coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,18,Ffine and warm during this period with
OL,19,Fplenty of sunny spells and light
OL,20,Fwinds. Chilly at times overnight with
OL,21,Fsome patchy overnight fog possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
